de.systemagmbh.interfaces
Interface ISysECDOffsets

All Known Implementing Classes:
ASysException
public interface ISysECDOffsets

This interface declares the offset values for the errorcodes used by the tool and component classes of Systema GmbH.

symbolic constant tool / component available numbers
ERROR_FREE all 1
ERROR_SYSTEM operating system 3000
ERROR_FATAL application 1000
ERROR_SERVICE services 100
ERROR_RESERVED project specific logic2900
ERROR_TOOLS free 200
ERROR_CONFIG configmanager 100
ERROR_LOGGER logger 100
ERROR_RESULTTABLEresulttable 100
ERROR_FILE filereader 100
ERROR_DBI database 500
ERROR_BUS messagebus 1000
ERROR_MESSAGE message 500

Version:
$Revision: 1.12 $
Author:
Herbert Helmstreit

Field Detail

ERROR_FREE

public static final int ERROR_FREE
This can be used to indicate that no error has occurred. The value is 0.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

ERROR_SYSTEM

public static final int ERROR_SYSTEM
Offset for errors concerning the operating system. Reserved values are 1 ... 2999.

Constant Field Values

ERROR_FATAL

public static final int ERROR_FATAL
3000-499.999 are reserved for SYSTEMA Components, modules and Standardapplications. FATAL-ERRORS range from 3000 ... 3999
